    <title>Manjaro 安装后的配置</title>
    <url>/2020/04/02/Manjaro-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>闲得无聊又把 Manjaro 装回来了。。正好这次做个笔记看都干了些啥。<br>仅适用于 Manjaro KDE，对于其他桌面环境仅供参考。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set Pacman Mirrors</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Add archlinuxcn repo</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo nano /etc/pacman.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Add following into the back of the file</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># [archlinuxcn]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># SigLevel = Optional TrustedOnly</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Server = https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/$arch</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Update repos &amp;&amp; Upgrade all packages</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syu archlinuxcn-keyring</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Upgrade kernel to latest linux-stable (which is 5.5 atm)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># linux55-nvidia-440xx is the driver for nvidia graphcis card (GTX 1070 here)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># headers and virtualbox-host-modules are optional</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S linux55 linux55-headers linux55-nvidia-440xx linux55-virtualbox-host-modules</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Remove old kernels (which is 5.4 atm)</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -Rs linux54 linux54-nvidia-440xx</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Fuck default folder named in Chinese</span></span><br><span class="line">nano .config/user-dirs.dirs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Edit the following lines:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_DESKTOP_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Desktop&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_DOWNLOAD_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Download&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_TEMPLATES_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Templates&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_PUBLICSHARE_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Public&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_DOCUMENTS_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Documents&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_MUSIC_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Music&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_PICTURES_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Pictures&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># XDG_VIDEOS_DIR=&quot;$HOME/Videos&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Then manually delete folders at $HOME and create</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## corresponding folders named in English</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># You should reboot now to apply folder name changes</span></span><br><span class="line">reboot</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Dividing Line</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;---------------------------------&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Apply themes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Install Adapta theme from official</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## repositories</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S adapta-kde adapta-gtk-theme</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Then manually set themes in system</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## settings. You can also downloads</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## other themes directly in system</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## settings</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Double click to open folders or files</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># in Dolphin:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 设置 - 工作空间行为 - 常规行为 - 点击行为 - 双击打开文件和文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># zsh &amp;&amp; oh-my-zsh &amp;&amp;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## As of Manjaro KDE 19.0.2, zsh is pre-installed,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## just install git and oh-my-zsh</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S git</span><br><span class="line">sh -c <span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## If forgot to set default term</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## DO NOT USE sudo HERE SINCE IT WILL CHANGE THE DEFAULT SHELL OF ROOT!!!</span></span><br><span class="line">chsh -s $(<span class="built_in">which</span> zsh)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## I prefer this config: https://github.com/caiogondim/bullet-train.zsh</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Place it in $ZSH_CUSTOM/themes, here $ZSH_CUSTOM == ~/.zsh</span></span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p ~/.zsh/themes</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Get bullet-train.zsh-theme in advance and locate to its position</span></span><br><span class="line">mv bullet-train.zsh-theme ~/.zsh/themes</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Edit ~/.zshrc</span></span><br><span class="line">nano ~/.zshrc</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Find ZSH_THEME and edit</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ZSH_THEME=&quot;bullet-train&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Find ZSH_CUSTOM and remove comments</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ZSH_CUSTOM=&quot;$HOME/.zsh&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Save the file.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Use trizen to install AUR packages</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S trizen</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Many would prefer yay but I am just used to trizen</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># But there you go</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Optional: To build Lineage OS, install dependencies</span></span><br><span class="line">trizen -S lineageos-devel</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Optional: a lot of fonts incoming</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Get cascadia code from https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code/releases</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## I prefer to download both versions, with or without powerline.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## And Sarasa Gothic from https://github.com/be5invis/Sarasa-Gothic/releases</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## then install them manually</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Then noto-fonts and adobe-source-han</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## (I know they are duplicated, but I&#x27;m fuckin&#x27; boring)</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S noto-fonts noto-fonts-cjk noto-fonts-emoji noto-fonts-extra</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-han-sans-otc-fonts adobe-source-han-serif-otc-fonts</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-code-pro-fonts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Miscellaneous fonts</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S wqy-microhei wqy-microhei-lite wqy-zenhei ttf-roboto ttf-dejavu ttf-wps-fonts</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Fcitx &amp;&amp; fcitx-sogoupinyin</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S fcitx-im kcm-fcitx fcitx-googlepinyin fcitx-skin-material</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Add profiles ~/.xprofile and reboot</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;export GTK_IM_MODULES=fcitx\n\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">export QT_IM_MODULES=fcitx\n\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">export XMODIFIERS=\&quot;@im=fcitx\&quot;&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; ~/.xprofile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Configure git</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Generate ssh key</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C <span class="string">&quot;eterocell@outlook.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S xclip</span><br><span class="line">xclip =sel clip &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Now ssh-key should have been copied to your paste board, set it in github</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Check connection</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Generate a GPG key</span></span><br><span class="line">gpg --full-gen-key</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Choose &quot;RSA and RSA&quot; &quot;keysize = 4096&quot; &quot;0 = key does not expire&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># List generated key</span></span><br><span class="line">gpg --list-secret-keys --keyid-format LONG</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># `sec` stands for &#x27;secret key&#x27;, ssb stands for &#x27;secret subkey&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># copy the public key and set in github</span></span><br><span class="line">gpg --armor --<span class="built_in">export</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;key ID which is after sec&#125;</span> | xclip --selection clipboard</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Then you can commit individual commits using</span></span><br><span class="line">git commit --gpg-sign=<span class="variable">$&#123;key ID which is after sec&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Or just set all commits sign with it</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.signinkey <span class="variable">$&#123;key ID which is after sec&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global commit.gpgsign <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># I&#x27;ve encrypted my SSH and GPG keys and stored online, convenient though risky</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Optional: Other packages</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S base-devel gcc gdb clang llvm vim google-chrome visual-studio-code-bin wps-office</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S nodejs npm maven gradle foxit-reader unrar unzip p7zip netease-cloud-music telegram-desktop</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S screenfetch neofetch</span><br><span class="line">trizen -S jetbrains-toolbox electron-ssr</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># I recommend electron-ssr from https://github.com/shadowsocksrr/electron-ssr/releases</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Which is still mantained</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Yoga C940 使用3个月后感想</title>
    <url>/2020/03/05/C940-3%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8E%E6%84%9F%E6%83%B3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>一直都想有一台带触控屏的 Windows 二合一笔记本，本来是非常心水 Surface Pro 的，但是看到 C940 的配置和价格之后我只想说——真香。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p>很早之前，大概还是 Windows 8 时期就听过以二合一闻名的 Yoga 系列，但是真正让我动了买二合一心思的还是 Surface Pro，至于理由，其实是肝舰 C。。。</p>
<p>当然，碍于学业还有钱包的问题，一直都没有买。而大学入学时，考虑到性能问题，最终入的还是 P775TM1-G 这种旅行重量重达将近 6kg 的大砖块。。因为几乎每天都要来往于实验室和宿舍，特别是晚上 21:30 摸完鱼回宿舍时还要背着那么重的电脑，最终压断了我为了省钱苦苦支撑的脊椎，开始考虑入手一台轻薄本。</p>
<p>最初，我仍然想选择 Surface Pro 7，但看到 C940 的评测之后几经考虑还是选择了 C940。</p>
<p>让我放弃苏菲的原因大概时以下几个：</p>
<ul>
<li>第七代的苏菲终于终于终于引入了 USB-C，只有一个，而且不是 Thunderbolt 3。。而 C940 有一个 USB-A，两个 Thunderbolt 3。</li>
<li>价格昂贵，苏菲在预想价位能买到 i5-1035G4，8GB 内存，256GB SSD（包含键盘盖和 Surface Pen）的型号。同价位的 C940 则有 i7-1065G7，16GB 内存，以及整整 1TB 的 PM981A。</li>
<li>苏菲被人吐槽很多的品控、售后等问题。</li>
</ul>
<p>最终，我下单了 C940。开箱时我就被它的外观惊艳到了——精巧的外观、机身摸起来顺滑的手感、深灰色的配色，以及最重要的，够轻够薄。</p>
<p>配置如下：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>CPU: Intel Core i7-1065G7 (4C8T, 1.5GHz Base, up to 3.9GHz)<br>Graphics: Intel Iris Plus 940 (64EUs)<br>RAM: 16GB LPDDR4X 3733MHz<br>Storage: 1TB NVMe PM981A<br>Screen: 14 inch 4K IPS (3840 x 2160, 16:9, HDR400)<br>Weight: 1.35kg</p>
</blockquote>
<p>对于一个轻薄本来说，这样的性能无疑是够用的。其中 i7-1065G7 作为 Ice Lake 10nm 的新产品，其性能让我很是期待，其 Cinebench R20 结果如下：</p>
<img src="/2020/03/05/C940-3%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8E%E6%84%9F%E6%83%B3/C940_CinebenchR20.png" class="" title="C940_CinebenchR20">

<p>多核性能已经接近 i7-6700HQ，CPU 性能是相当不错的。至于 Iris Plus 性能有多强我倒是不太关注，至少对于一般桌面应用在 4K 分辨率下的表现我还是很满意的。</p>
<p>说到 4K 就不得不说一下这块屏幕。3840 x 2160 的 IPS，支持十点触控，支持手写笔（笔记本内置一个 4096 级压感的）。从网上找到的参数:</p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>86.5% DCI-P3 色域以及 98.8% sRGB 色域</li>
<li>最高亮度 550 nits</li>
<li>对比度 1478:1</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p>高分屏给我带来的最直观的观感便是 Windows 在 1080p 奥利给一样的字体渲染明显改善。。终于可以摆脱 Mactype 这种有时候会明显拖慢速度的不完美解法了。</p>
<p>再说说实际日常体验。</p>
<p>从去年 12 月初购买，到现在已有 3 个月的使用，日常就是 JetBrains 系的 IDE，VSCode 之类的编辑器。除此之外还有较简单的笔记、网页、视频等轻量任务，其余较重的任务都交给 P775TM1-G 的 i7-8700k、32GB 内存完成了。可以说 i7-1065G7 和 16GB 内存基本完美满足了我对轻薄本的性能要求。</p>
<p>续航是本机最大的槽点之一。4K 屏的耗电量是真的有点高。。正常浏览网页、写代码什么的能坚持 3-5 小时不等，可以说续航并不优秀。</p>
<p>除此之外，Sound-Bar 绝对是本机又一大亮点。配合 Dolby Atmos，外放质量足够好。当然和我的 XBA-Z5 以及 WH-1000XM2 比起来肯定还是逊色很多的（废话，这么比根本不公平）。</p>
<p>总结：<br>优点：</p>
<ul>
<li>外观、机身工艺一流</li>
<li>非常有优势的价格</li>
<li>两个满血 Thunderbolt 3 接口</li>
<li>爽到的 4K 屏</li>
<li>16GB 内存相对于 8GB 的提升真的很明显</li>
</ul>
<p>特点：</p>
<ul>
<li>i7-1065G7 对我来说够用的性能。</li>
<li>虽然单纯的触控在 Windows 下体验非常糟糕，但是触控的存在对于单纯的键鼠操作还是起到了锦上添花二点作用。</li>
<li>键盘手感还不错</li>
<li>我用不到的 Wi-Fi 6</li>
</ul>
<p>缺点：</p>
<ul>
<li>即使内置了 60Wh 的大电池，续航依然不尽如人意</li>
<li>有时机身温度较高</li>
<li>键盘方向键反人类设计</li>
</ul>
<p>综合来说，这是让我非常满意的一台二合一笔记本。价格便宜（相对来说），强劲的性能（相对来说），优质的屏幕（4K 触控），锦上添花的特点（Sound-Bar），还有联想的品控和售后，这款产品在相对小众的二合一市场中注定拥有它的一席之地。</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>TechColumn</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>C940</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>[数学][水题] HDU 2674 &quot;N! Again&quot;</title>
    <url>/2020/02/08/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6-%E6%B0%B4%E9%A2%98-HDU-2674-N-Again/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="原题链接"><a href="#原题链接" class="headerlink" title="原题链接"></a>原题链接</h2><p><a href="http://acm.hdu.edu.cn/showproblem.php?pid=2674">HDU</a>, <a href="https://vjudge.net/problem/HDU-2674">Virtual Judge</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<hr>
<h2 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h2><blockquote>
<p>WhereIsHeroFrom: Zty, what are you doing ?<br>Zty: I want to calculate N!……<br>WhereIsHeroFrom: So easy! How big N is ?<br>Zty: 1 &lt;=N &lt;=1000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000…<br>WhereIsHeroFrom: Oh! You must be crazy! Are you Fa Shao?<br>Zty: No. I haven’s finished my saying. I just said I want to calculate N! mod 2009</p>
<p>Hint : 0! = 1, N! = N*(N-1)!</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Input"><a href="#Input" class="headerlink" title="Input"></a>Input</h3><blockquote>
<p>Each line will contain one integer N(0 &lt;= N&lt;=10^9). Process to end of file.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Output"><a href="#Output" class="headerlink" title="Output"></a>Output</h3><blockquote>
<p>For each case, output N! mod 2009</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Sample-Input"><a href="#Sample-Input" class="headerlink" title="Sample Input"></a>Sample Input</h3><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Sample-Output"><a href="#Sample-Output" class="headerlink" title="Sample Output"></a>Sample Output</h3><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="原思路"><a href="#原思路" class="headerlink" title="原思路"></a>原思路</h2><p>已知 2009! 因为有因数 2009 =&gt; 2009! mod 2009 == 0。因而包括 2009! 及以后的阶乘模 2009 结果必为 0，则只需算 2009 之前的。</p>
<h3 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> num;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; num) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> sum = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (num &lt; <span class="number">2009</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= num; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                sum *= i;</span><br><span class="line">                sum %= <span class="number">2009</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; sum &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="number">0</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="改进思路"><a href="#改进思路" class="headerlink" title="改进思路"></a>改进思路</h2><p>因为 2009 = 41 x 7 x 7，因而到 49 及以后的数的阶乘结果都将为 0.</p>
<h3 id="改进后的-Code"><a href="#改进后的-Code" class="headerlink" title="改进后的 Code"></a>改进后的 Code</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> num;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; num) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> sum = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (num &lt; <span class="number">49</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= num; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                sum *= i;</span><br><span class="line">                sum %= <span class="number">2009</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; sum &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="number">0</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
