  <entry>
    <title>使用 VSCode 和 MinGW 实现 Windows C/C++ 开发</title>
    <url>/2020/02/10/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-VSCode-%E5%92%8C-MinGW-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0-Windows-C-C-%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://nuwen.net/mingw.html">MinGW Distro</a></p>
<p><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">VSCode</a></p>
<p><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/cpp/config-mingw">官方文档</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<hr>
<ul>
<li><p>下载并安装 VSCode</p>
</li>
<li><p>在 VSCode 中安装 C/C++ 插件</p>
</li>
<li><p>下载并安装 MinGW Distro，将其解压至 C:\Program Files\MinGW</p>
</li>
<li><p>打开 cmd 输入以下命令添加环境变量</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">setx /M <span class="built_in">path</span> &quot;<span class="variable">%PATH%</span>;C:\Program Files\MinGW\bin\&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>重启 cmd 输入以下命令以检查环境变量是否正确添加</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">g++ --version</span><br><span class="line">gdb --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>正确添加环境变量后，打开 VSCode，选择存放 C/C++ 代码的文件夹，新建 HelloWorld 文件夹并在其中新建 HelloWorld.cpp 文件并保存</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>在终端中输入以下命令创建工作区</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">code .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><p>点击终端-运行生成任务，选择 C/C++:g++.exe build active file，你会发现 VSCode 在工作区目录中创建了 .vscode 文件夹以及其中的 tasks.json</p>
</li>
<li><p>点击调试-启动调试，选择 C++ (GDB/LLDB)，选择 g++.exe build and debug active file，你会发现 VSCode 在 .vscode 文件夹中创建了 launch.json</p>
</li>
<li><p>可以生成和调试之后，如果想更多修改 C/C++ 插件的设置，可以按 Ctrl+Shift+P 搜索 C/C++: 编辑配置，这将在 .vscode 文件夹中创建 c_cpp_properties.json 文件继而修改配置，修改 C/C++ 标准便是在这一步进行。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>2020.7.20 更新：使用<code>clangd</code>扩展获得更好的 <strong>静态代码检查</strong> 和 <strong>代码补全</strong> 体验，同时与 MS 官方提供的 <code>C/C++</code> 插件共存，获得最佳的 <strong>调试</strong> 与 <strong>直接运行</strong> 体验</p>
<ul>
<li>安装 <code>llvm</code> 工具链，包括 <code>clang</code>, <code>clangd</code>, <code>clang-tidy</code> 等工具</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Windows with Scoop package manager</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install llvm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><p>在 VSCode 中安装 <code>clangd</code> 插件</p>
</li>
<li><p>在 VSCode 的 <code>settings.json</code> 中调整以下设置</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 关闭 C/C++ 插件提供的静态代码检查与补全功能， clang-tidy 提供的体验更好</span></span><br><span class="line">&quot;C_Cpp.intelliSenseEngine&quot;: &quot;Disabled&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;C_Cpp.autocomplete&quot;: &quot;Disabled&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">&quot;C_Cpp.errorSquiggles&quot;: &quot;Disabled&quot;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>Enjoy</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>WorkTips</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>开发环境</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>[博弈][水题] HDU 6312 &quot;Game&quot;</title>
    <url>/2020/02/08/%E5%8D%9A%E5%BC%88-%E6%B0%B4%E9%A2%98-HDU-6312-Game/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="原题链接"><a href="#原题链接" class="headerlink" title="原题链接"></a>原题链接</h2><p><a href="http://acm.hdu.edu.cn/showproblem.php?pid=6312">HDU</a>, <a href="https://vjudge.net/problem/HDU-6312">Virtual Judge</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<hr>
<h2 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h2><blockquote>
<p>Alice and Bob are playing a game.<br>The game is played on a set of positive integers from 1 to n.<br>In one step, the player can choose a positive integer from the set, and erase all of its divisors from the set. If a divisor doesn’t exist it will be ignored.<br>Alice and Bob choose in turn, the one who cannot choose (current set is empty) loses.<br>Alice goes first, she wanna know whether she can win. Please judge by outputing ‘Yes’ or ‘No’.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Input"><a href="#Input" class="headerlink" title="Input"></a>Input</h3><blockquote>
<p>There might be multiple test cases, no more than 10. You need to read till the end of input.<br>For each test case, a line containing an integer n. (1≤n≤500)</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Output"><a href="#Output" class="headerlink" title="Output"></a>Output</h3><blockquote>
<p>A line for each test case, ‘Yes’ or ‘No’.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Sample-Input"><a href="#Sample-Input" class="headerlink" title="Sample Input"></a>Sample Input</h3><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Sample-Output"><a href="#Sample-Output" class="headerlink" title="Sample Output"></a>Sample Output</h3><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h2><p><del>说实话这题是找出前几个的解后直接蒙的</del></p>
<h2 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> num;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; num) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Yes&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>OJ记录</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>OJ</tag>
        <tag>HDU</tag>
        <tag>水题</tag>
        <tag>博弈</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>编译Android Linux Kernel并生成Flashable Zip</title>
    <url>/2020/04/06/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91Android-Linux-Kernel%E5%B9%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90Flashable-Zip/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>适用于 Android 10, ARM 64</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="Clone-所需的-Repository"><a href="#Clone-所需的-Repository" class="headerlink" title="Clone 所需的 Repository"></a>Clone 所需的 Repository</h2><h3 id="Clone-kernel-repo"><a href="#Clone-kernel-repo" class="headerlink" title="Clone kernel repo"></a>Clone kernel repo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/ExampleUser/ExampleRepo.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Clone-toolchains"><a href="#Clone-toolchains" class="headerlink" title="Clone toolchains"></a>Clone toolchains</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Clang_Google</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://android.googlesource.com/platform/prebuilts/clang/host/linux-x86</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># GCC_Google_ARM32</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://android.googlesource.com/platform/prebuilts/gcc/linux-x86/arm/arm-linux-androideabi-4.9</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># GCC_Google_ARM64</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://android.googlesource.com/platform/prebuilts/gcc/linux-x86/aarch64/aarch64-linux-android-4.9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Clone-AnyKernel3"><a href="#Clone-AnyKernel3" class="headerlink" title="Clone AnyKernel3"></a>Clone AnyKernel3</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/osm0sis/AnyKernel3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="确认-defconfig"><a href="#确认-defconfig" class="headerlink" title="确认 defconfig"></a>确认 defconfig</h2><p>比如说 arm64 的内核的 defconfig 一般在 arch/arm64/configs</p>
<h2 id="编译内核"><a href="#编译内核" class="headerlink" title="编译内核"></a>编译内核</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;Your Kernel Path&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="清理编译环境"><a href="#清理编译环境" class="headerlink" title="清理编译环境"></a>清理编译环境</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">make clean &amp;&amp; make mrproper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="准备编译环境"><a href="#准备编译环境" class="headerlink" title="准备编译环境"></a>准备编译环境</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir -p out</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> ARCH=arm64</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> CLANG_PATH=<span class="variable">$&#123;Your Clang_Google Path&#125;</span>/<span class="variable">$&#123;Prefered Clang Version&#125;</span>/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="variable">$&#123;CLANG_PATH&#125;</span>:<span class="variable">$&#123;PATH&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> CLANG_TRIPLE=aarch64-linux-gnu-</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> CROSS_COMPILE=<span class="variable">$&#123;Your GCC_Google_ARM64 Path&#125;</span>/bin/aarch64-linux-android-</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> CROSS_COMPILE_ARM32=<span class="variable">$&#123;Your GCC_Google_ARM32 Path&#125;</span>/bin/arm-linux-androideabi-</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> LD_LIBRARY_PATH=~<span class="variable">$&#123;Your Clang_Google Path&#125;</span>/<span class="variable">$&#123;Prefered Clang Version&#125;</span>/lib64:<span class="variable">$LD_LIBRARY_PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="设置-defconfig"><a href="#设置-defconfig" class="headerlink" title="设置 defconfig"></a>设置 defconfig</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">make CC=clang AR=llvm-ar NM=llvm-nm OBJCOPY=llvm-objcopy STRIP=llvm-strip O=out <span class="variable">$&#123;defconfig name&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="开始编译"><a href="#开始编译" class="headerlink" title="开始编译"></a>开始编译</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">make CC=clang AR=llvm-ar NM=llvm-nm OBJCOPY=llvm-objcopy STRIP=llvm-strip O=out -j<span class="variable">$&#123;$(nproc --all) / 2&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="用-AnyKernel-生成-Flashable-Zip"><a href="#用-AnyKernel-生成-Flashable-Zip" class="headerlink" title="用 AnyKernel 生成 Flashable Zip"></a>用 AnyKernel 生成 Flashable Zip</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp <span class="variable">$&#123;Your Kernel Path/out/arch/arm64/boot/Image.gz-dtb&#125;</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;Your AnyKernel3 Path&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;Your AnyKernel3 Path&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">zip -r9 flashable.zip * -x .git README.md *placeholder</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>需要注意的是 AnyKernel 需要一定的改动才能生成 Flashable Zip，详见官方文档。</p>
]]></content>
